author: The Current
description:
Dessa describes her fascination with layered vocals
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube or hit the Thanks button

Dessa describes how she landed on the idea of including a round of the folk song "Frère Jacques" in the outro of her original song, "Camelot."

Dessa's 2025 double-sided single "Camelot" / "Tough Call" is available on @DoomtreeRecords.
